/********************************
* Replace Checkbox plugin
* 
* by Mike Behnke
*
* Description: Basic plugin to create a link to use in place of a checkbox.  
* Styles for the checked/non-checked state should be defined in a stylesheet, 
* the plugin mearly changes the class and keeps the checkbox updated.
*
* usage: $(function(){ $(".checkbox").replaceCheckbox(); });
*
* options: 
*   {
*		toggleClass: "toggle",
*		checkedClass: "checked"
*	}
*
********************************/